data.description: 11/25/23 1-3pm Open House. Beautiful surroundings yet close to town this cottage-style home sits on 5.24 gorgeous acres, mostly flat & gently sloped with same level access to home from driveway! 2 bedrooms & 1 Full bath with roomy living room, & indoor laundry room! Kitchen area has tons of natural light & storage! Conveniently located near stores, Ft Vannoy Elementary, & other services, this home has fully fenced yard area, newer roof & windows, & is set back from road. Large garage/shop space on lower level can drive too from outside or use stairs inside home. Floorplan, Maps & property boundaries on MLS. DO NOT ENTER PROPERTY OR GO DOWN DRIVEWAY WITHOUT APPOINTMENT! Open House Saturday 11/25/23 1-3pm. Estate is local & can review offers quickly. Estate may give preference to offers that take property ''As-Is'' including some possessions &/or no clean up.
